headline: OMNICOM TO PRESENT AT THE MORGAN STANLEY TECHNOLOGY, MEDIA & TELECOM CONFERENCE
summary: Omnicom Group Inc. (NYSE: OMC) today announced that it will present at the Morgan Stanley Global Technology, Media & Telecom Conference in San Francisco, California on Tuesday, March 4, 2025 at 10:00 a.m. Pacific Time. Live and archived webcasts will be available at the investor relations section of www.omnicomgroup.com.
